{"tid":584994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"王毅怒斥「精日」分子：中國人的敗類！","createTime":"2018-03-08T09:14:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T05:24:31.000Z","uid":39464,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"008053d6ee1bd6542503145ed4d4d97712e911c6","tid":584994,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T09:14:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180308/large/1520494877_fabd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180308%2Flarge%2F1520494877_fabd.jpg&h=7d98b409&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日有網民大肆侮辱南京大屠殺的死者，被稱為「精日」分子。正在北京出席全國兩會的外交部長王毅，今日在結束記者會時，有記者問他如何看待這些「精日」分子時，王毅怒斥：「中國人的敗類！」<br />\n<br />\n多名網民近日穿着二戰時日本軍服，在各地的抗日遺址、愛國教育基地等拍照留令，再將照片放到網上，被網民怒斥是「精神日本人」，簡稱「精日」分子。王毅今日被內地記者詢問，他如何看待這些人的行為時，正在離開記者會場的王毅停位了腳步，一臉嚴肅的對着提問的記者說：「中國人的敗類！」<br />\n<br />\n早前，兩名穿着日軍軍服的男子，在南京保衞戰遺址合影，被南京警方行政拘留15日，另一名男子則在南京大屠殺紀念館拍攝短片，被警方以尋釁滋事，行政拘留8日。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180308/57919799\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180308%2F57919799&d=XZKGZzH3RpoVKciqCDwveMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=aedc9163\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180308%2F57919799&h=6bf85264\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180308/57919799</a>"},{"pid":"64493eaf4b9bc6ee759f562456e044d3b7f1e2c5","tid":584994,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T09:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff64e8255926b6477a5ff6e6c8fb2944255fa54f","tid":584994,"uid":52062,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T09:15:56.000Z","msg":"好撚小氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":